<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٦٢٤ - أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6014">‌مَحْمُودُ بْنُ غَيْلَانَ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2594">‌أَبُو دَاوُدَ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">‌شُعْبَةُ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/119">‌إِبْرَاهِيمَ بْنِ مَيْسَرَةَ </a>،<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٣٠٥⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2980">‌طَاوُسٍ </a>، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">‌ابْنِ عُمَرَ </a>أَنَّ رَسُولَ اللهِ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ <span class="c2">«نَهَى عَنِ الدُّبَّاءِ»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>